<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̹tbnạny rḍy by</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̹tbnạny rḍy byã .. wạsẖtrạny ḥn ʿlyã
 1- (bqạly fy ḥḍnh mkạn .. wnsyt ạ̉yạm ạlḥrmạn)2
 dạ ạ̉hly wʿylty kmạn .. wrạsmạly
 2- (ạbn lyã sẖạ̉n kbyr .. ạ̉bwyạ ybqy̱ ạlqdyr)2
 ạ̹zạy ạ̉kẖạf ạ̉nạ mn ạlsẖryr .. mhmạ jạny
 3- (nsạny ạlmạḍy ạlạ̉lym .. kẖly̱ lsạny yqwl trnym)2
 gẖslny bdmh ạlkrym .. wfdạny
 4- (ʿwḍ ʿn kl ạlly rạḥ .. wḍmd kl ạljrạḥ)2
 wywmạty ạ̉ʿysẖ ạ̉frạḥ .. wạ̉gẖạny
 5- (tʿạlwạ sẖwfwạ yạ nạs .. yswʿ ạ̹dạny ạlkẖlạṣ)2
 mạsẖy mʿạh mrfwʿ ạlrạs .. ʿly̱ mqạmy
 6- (hạʿysẖ lh ṭwl ạlsnyn .. ạbn kẖạḍʿ wạ̉myn)2
 wlạ ạ̉ḥyd ʿnh sẖmạl wymyn .. ṭwl ạ̉yạmy</lyrics>
<author>ṣmwỷyl mnsy</author>
<hymn_number>9603</hymn_number>
</song>